         VERSION=1.3.2
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:f2f4dca05a93d32089e53a0e1434b36fbbee6caedfb4107e1b51880d3b48e27d8b535344765ef0b165826aa9ad473260509df050cc416875943f641c68a2031c
